{"tid":886254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【全城譁然】支那高鐵男狂吻幼女 警方：父女關係 不算猥褻","createTime":"2018-11-02T03:13:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T12:35:54.000Z","uid":89543,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"52e05f4e32d7103dbb786f1b6e199851617ef08a","tid":886254,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T03:13:20.000Z","msg":"有內地女網民上月27日在江西南昌乘坐高鐵時，發現一名男子竟將手伸進年幼女童的衣服內亂摸，更掀起女童上衣，不斷親吻她的背部和頸項，甚至伸手進她的內褲中。女童極力反抗說：「爸爸不要」，惟男子沒有停手。當時影片曝光後，即引來極大迴響，網民狂轟男子行為過火。南昌鐵路警方見事態嚴重，成立調查小組查明事件，豈料結果出爐，指當事人是父女「不構成猥褻」。上至官媒，及至愛心團體、明星、網民，都炮轟判斷不公！<br />\n<br />\n南昌鐵路公安局在10月31日晚發佈簡短通報稱，「針對網傳『G1402次列車發生疑似猥褻女童』視頻引起媒體和網友關注一事，南昌鐵路警方高度重視，立即組織進行調查，現已查明視頻中當事人周XX（男，30歲）與小女孩（5歲）是父女關係，視頻中周XX行為不構成猥褻違法」。<br />\n<br />\n豈料這個結果又再一次掀起社會怒火。官媒央視首當其衝，直斥「這樣的結論太敷衍」！評論稱，影片之所以引起極高關注度，因為事件觸碰到公眾最敏感的神經－－「幼童保護」，「一句簡單的『當事人為父女關係，視頻中周XX的行為不構成猥褻違法』」，怕是難以平息公眾的質疑與猜測。<br />\n<br />\n央視評論引述網民意見指出，「此二人為父女」並不構成「周XX行為不構成猥褻違法」的必然因果條件，並引中國少年兒童文化藝術基金會「女童保護」基金統計指出，2017年全年媒體公開報道的性侵兒童案中，加害人為家庭成員，包括父親、哥哥、繼父、祖父的案件一共有32宗，佔性侵兒童案的15.31%。"},{"pid":"b4d6f1a4351288b2b2e14e8dee02be0b498909cf","tid":886254,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T03:31:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"336cd1c34ee962f8197d67a837750779fc5f4e06","tid":886254,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T03:34:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e8a601453128e58cbcda8e5727a7be244edd288","tid":886254,"uid":131441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T03:35:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"92d2b9c69e017106ffa8217cbf27c87cdb69dcb6","tid":886254,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T03:47:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/K7E3Aw4brMM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FK7E3Aw4brMM&d=1VJWldnTnQw7AQGwQpx2r%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=7c32e777\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/K7E3Aw4brMM</a><br />\n<br />\n諗起呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e7d03da7412bda40120bb85ec5033a1112634a1","tid":886254,"uid":218490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T06:06:42.000Z","msg":"臭雞"},{"pid":"fa334179a68907ef926cd8b3dd0de287702491e3","tid":886254,"uid":1672,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T06:10:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oVtqm6r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoVtqm6r.png&h=d4a2f878&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d6caf295528ec6073960a3c22940850cca0e0070","tid":886254,"uid":52942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T06:15:18.000Z","msg":"你對一個戴套就唔當強姦既國家仲有咩期望"},{"pid":"9db54377c370883e03bccd159956c5cf7037b778","tid":886254,"uid":154725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T07:09:36.000Z","msg":"唔計"},{"pid":"f2d8c6df9d2e71c7431fb505518f09476cdecd61","tid":886254,"uid":168368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T12:27:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b456419871c9aabdef06f25caf0babcc720fcb1","tid":886254,"uid":168368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T12:30:29.000Z","msg":"收皮啦女權西"},{"pid":"eb02d56c2c0a88beeb5065125c5cfcfa7eddd9bf","tid":886254,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b456419871c9aabdef06f25caf0babcc720fcb1","tid":886254,"uid":168368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T12:30:29.000Z","msg":"收皮啦女權西"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T12:31:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"095633a54f649c53cb5d9f2e26acb75e301f21a3","tid":886254,"uid":70060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T12:35:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}